This repo is configured as fork of: https://github.com/apexcharts/apexcharts.js

Primary apexcharts reporsitory (https://github.com/apexcharts/apexcharts.js) is configured as upstream repo for this project (https://github.com/it-xtech-dev/apexcharts.js)

https://digitaldrummerj.me/git-syncing-fork-with-original-repo/

Development:
1. Compile in watch mode (open terminal window and write): npm run dev
2. Open one of the samples from samples folder eg: samples\vanilla-js\area\area-datetime.html
3. Every time you change the code and save it will quickly recompiled
4. Refresh browser window to debug new code.

Build:
1. In Visual Studio Code Terminal: npm run build

Packaging:
1. In Visual Studio Code Terminal: npm pack